            <p class="muted" style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> you@domain.com</p>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>GitHub:</strong> github.com/JWormgoor</p>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 8px 0;">
